                        स्वाविद्यापदतत्कार्यं श्रीचक्रोपरि भासुरम् ।<br>
                        बिन्दुरूपशिवाकारं रामचन्द्रपदं भजे ॥
                    </div>
                    <div class="english text-center text-lg text-gray-700 italic">
                        I worship the feet of Rama Chandra, which are the essence of Shiva,<br>
                        Shining upon the Shri Chakra, the cause of one's own knowledge.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
