        <!-- Peace Invocation -->
        <section class="mb-12">
            <div class="mantra-highlight rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8">
                <div class="sanskrit text-center text-2xl leading-relaxed">
                    ॐ भद्रं कर्णेभिः शृणुयाम देवा ।<br>
                    भद्रं पश्येमाक्षभिर्यजत्राः ।<br>
                    स्थिरैरङ्गैस्तुष्टुवाꣳसस्तनूभिः ।<br>
                    व्यशेम देवहितं यदायुः ।<br>
                    स्वस्ति न इन्द्रो वृद्धश्रवाः ।<br>
                    स्वस्ति नः पूषा विश्ववेदाः ।<br>
                    स्वस्ति नस्तार्क्ष्योऽरिष्टनेमिः ।<br>
                    स्वस्ति नो बृहस्पतिर्दधातु ।<br>
                    ॐ शान्तिः शान्तिः शान्तिः ॥
                </div>
                <div class="english text-center mt-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
                    Om, may we hear with our ears what is auspicious, O Devas!<br>
                    May we see with our eyes what is auspicious, O worshipful ones!<br>
                    May we, with firm limbs and bodies, offering praise,<br>
                    Enjoy the life allotted by the Devas.<br>
                    May Indra of ancient fame be auspicious to us!<br>
                    May Pushan, the all-knowing, be auspicious to us!<br>
                    May Tarkshya, who destroys evil, be auspicious to us!<br>
                    May Brihaspati bestow upon us auspiciousness!<br>
                    Om, peace, peace, peace!
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

