            <p class="text-amber-100 mb-4">May we hear auspiciousness with our ears, O Divine Ones</p>
            <div class="border-t border-amber-700 pt-4 mt-4">
                <p class="text-sm">Sacred Text of Bhavanopanishad | भावनोपनिषत्</p>
